plot: The group works together to free the 7th Messenger from a secret government facility. Joshua's latest visions indicate a new threat is underway.

The limits of each Messenger's power are put to the test as they work together to free a key player from a secret government lock-up, and Joshua's (Jon Fletcher) latest vision points to the appearance of a treacherous new enemy. Diogo Morgado, Shantel VanSanten, Craig Frank, JD Pardo, Sofia Black D'Elia, Anna Diop and Joel Courtney star.
